# Committed example reports — 3+ MB single-file HTML each, dominated by
# inlined minified asset bytes (Sakura / jQuery / DataTables / Mermaid).
# Mark `-diff` so `git diff` shows "Binary files differ" instead of a
# many-thousand-line unreadable wall of CSS/JS noise; the
# `example-report-up-to-date` CI job is the real change detector.
examples/*.html -diff linguist-generated
